---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About — GEO China" description="GEO China is the #1 Chinese resource for Generative Engine Optimization. We bridge the gap between global GEO methodologies and the Chinese AI search ecosystem." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header lang="en" />
		<main>
			<section class="page-header">
				<div class="section-label"><span class="label-dot"></span> About</div>
				<h1>About GEO China</h1>
			</section>

			<section class="about-grid">
				<div class="about-main">
					<p class="lead">
						GEO China (geochina.co) is the <strong>first systematic GEO learning platform</strong> in the Chinese internet.
					</p>

					<h2>What We Do</h2>
					<p>
						GEO (Generative Engine Optimization) is the new paradigm of search optimization in the AI era.
						As more users turn to ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overview for information,
						traditional SEO is no longer enough.
					</p>
					<p>
						We study the methodologies of GEO pioneers (Princeton research team, Jason Barnard, Kevin Indig, Lily Ray),
						validate them through real-world implementation, and translate our findings for the Chinese community.
					</p>

					<h2>Why China Focus</h2>
					<p>
						While tools like Semrush and Ahrefs cover English GEO, the Chinese market has its own unique AI search ecosystem:
						Baidu Wenxin, Doubao, Kimi, and Tongyi Qianwen. These platforms have entirely different citation logic
						that requires specialized research and strategy.
					</p>
					<p>
						GEO China is the only Chinese resource that covers both international and domestic AI search engines.
					</p>

					<h2>Content Focus</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>🔬 <strong>Methodology Deep-dives</strong> — Analyzing GEO pioneer frameworks</li>
						<li>📊 <strong>Weekly GEO Reports</strong> — China market AI citation data</li>
						<li>🧪 <strong>GEO Lab</strong> — Real experiments on live websites, open data</li>
						<li>🔧 <strong>Tutorials</strong> — Citation Triggers, Schema, AI crawler config</li>
						<li>🛠️ <strong>Tool Reviews</strong> — GEO tool evaluation and comparison</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>Contact</h2>
					<p>
						Email: <a href="mailto:hello@geochina.co">hello@geochina.co</a><br/>
						Web: <a href="https://geochina.co">geochina.co</a>
					</p>
				</div>
				<aside class="about-sidebar">
					<div class="sidebar-card">
						<h3>GEO at a Glance</h3>
						<p>GEO = Getting AI search engines to cite your content.</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Princeton research: GEO boosts AI visibility by <strong>40%</strong></li>
							<li>AI referral converts at <strong>5×</strong> traditional search</li>
							<li>ChatGPT has <strong>800M+</strong> weekly active users</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="sidebar-card">
						<h3>Services</h3>
						<p>We offer GEO audits, brand optimization, and global expansion packages.</p>
						<a href="/en/services">View Services →</a>
					</div>
				</aside>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer lang="en" />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.page-header { padding: 3em 0 2em; }
	.page-header h1 { margin-top: 0.5em; }
	.section-label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
	.label-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--black); display: inline-block; }
	.about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 4em; padding-bottom: 4em; }
	.about-main { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 2em; }
	.lead { font-size: 1.25em; color: var(--text) !important; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 2em; }
	.about-main h2 { font-size: 1.4em; margin-top: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.4em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); }
	.about-main p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.85; }
	.about-main ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; }
	.about-main li { padding: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); }
	.about-main li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
	.about-sidebar { padding-top: 2em; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5em; }
	.sidebar-card { background: var(--bg-section); padding: 2em; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); }
	.sidebar-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
	.sidebar-card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; }
	.sidebar-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0 0; }
	.sidebar-card li { font-size: 14px; padding: 6px 0; color: var(--text-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
	.sidebar-card li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
	.sidebar-card a { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); }
	@media (max-width: 720px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2em; } }
</style>
